.SH Law #3: Who Cares?
\(lqImpact\(rq is a fluff word.
.PP
People say \(lqimpact\(rq the way astrologers say \(lqenergy\(rq: a
vague scalar that is always supposed to be \(lqhigher\(rq than last
year.
It sounds serious.
It explains nothing.
.PP
Under KarmaRank, \(lqimpact\(rq has a very specific implementation:
.RS
.PP
\f[B]Impact = Who Cares?\f[R]
.RE
.PP
Literally: who (S_i) cares (k_i).
.IP \(bu 2
\(lqWho\(rq = which people in the field have non\-zero Status with
respect to your rating.
.IP \(bu 2
