version.\f[R] Before I draft the RFC, can I get your mental model on how
\f[I]you\f[R] would structure the lock\-free queue?\(rq
.IP \(bu 2
\f[B]The IKEA Payoff:\f[R] They give you a technical constraint.
When you implement it, they see their own genius in your code.
.PP
\f[B]Target: The Politician Witness\f[R]
.IP \(bu 2
\f[B]The Hook (Strategic Alignment):\f[R] \(lqI\(cqm scoping [Project
Y].
I know this overlaps with the VP\(cqs `Efficiency' pillar.
How would you frame this so it lands best with the Director during the
