.SS Phase 2: Write The Test (The Spec)
Now that you have validated the demand and secured a Witness, you enter
the \f[B]Red State\f[R].
.PP
Open a blank document.
Write the bullet point exactly as you want it to appear in your
promotion packet six months from now.
.RS
.PP
